  "title": "Commis Chef",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities</p><p>•</p><p>Prepare and execute dishes from your assigned section with precision, consistency, and high presentation standards.</p><p>•</p><p>Assist the Chef de Partie in mise en place, service, and kitchen cleanliness.</p><p>•</p><p>Uphold hygiene and safety standards according to SFA and internal SOPs.</p><p>•</p><p>Communicate effectively with team members to ensure smooth kitchen workflow.</p><p>•</p><p>Participate in daily prep, service, and post-service duties with a proactive and professional attitude.</p><p>•</p><p>Receive and store deliveries properly, maintaining stock rotation and quality checks.</p><p>Requirements</p><p>•</p><p>Minimum 1 years of kitchen experience in a refined or upscale restaurant setting.</p><p>•</p><p>Basic knife skills and understanding of mise en place systems.</p><p>•</p><p>Strong work ethic, adaptability, and attention to detail.</p><p>•</p><p>Good communication skills and ability to work well under pressure.<br /><br />Maxhunt Resource Pte Ltd | EA Licence: 22C1322Cynthia Lai | Registration No: R25146301</p>",
